1
00:00:00,500 --> 00:00:04,129
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

2
00:00:04,209 --> 00:00:05,649
<Default><b>[flag fluttering]</b></Default>

3
00:00:07,469 --> 00:00:08,949
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Motoyasu?</b></Default>

4
00:00:10,970 --> 00:00:12,696
<Default><b>[MIRELIA] He's searching
for his comrades</b></Default>

5
00:00:12,720 --> 00:00:13,786
<Default><b>who split up with him</b></Default>

6
00:00:13,810 --> 00:00:15,616
<Default><b>after the Spirit Tortoise
fight.</b></Default>

7
00:00:15,640 --> 00:00:17,520
<Default><b>We have located
one of them.</b></Default>

8
00:00:17,640 --> 00:00:18,995
<Default><b>If our intel's correct</b></Default>

9
00:00:19,019 --> 00:00:21,419
<Default><b>then they're in small town
near Melromarc.</b></Default>

10
00:00:21,690 --> 00:00:23,050
<Default><b>Near Melromarc?</b></Default>

11
00:00:23,649 --> 00:00:26,009
<Default><b>Right. And the whereabouts
of the others?</b></Default>

12
00:00:26,190 --> 00:00:27,830
<Default><b>We haven't got a clue.</b></Default>

13
00:00:28,070 --> 00:00:29,399
<Default><b>Mal...</b></Default>

14
00:00:30,359 --> 00:00:32,999
<Default><b>Bitch hasn't shown herself
since we last talked.</b></Default>

15
00:00:33,280 --> 00:00:35,055
<Default><b>The last sighting
reported of her</b></Default>

16
00:00:35,079 --> 00:00:36,999
<Default><b>was near the
northern border.</b></Default>

17
00:00:37,039 --> 00:00:39,385
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] You can't use
her slave crest to find her?</b></Default>

18
00:00:39,409 --> 00:00:40,606
<Default><b>[MIRELIA] We've tried</b></Default>

19
00:00:40,630 --> 00:00:42,950
<Default><b>but she's somehow
blocking our attempts.</b></Default>

20
00:00:43,170 --> 00:00:44,410
<Default><b>It's no use.</b></Default>

21
00:00:45,549 --> 00:00:47,460
<Default><b>And the other heroes?</b></Default>

22
00:00:48,380 --> 00:00:50,640
<Default><b>Ren and Itsuki
remain to be seen.</b></Default>

23
00:00:51,179 --> 00:00:53,140
<Default><b>However, one thing</b></Default>

24
00:00:53,219 --> 00:00:55,286
<Default><b>about the Sword Hero's
been confirmed.</b></Default>

25
00:00:55,310 --> 00:00:57,366
<Default><b>His companions have been
pronounced dead.</b></Default>

26
00:00:57,390 --> 00:00:58,430
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

27
00:00:58,939 --> 00:01:00,140
<Default><b>Sir Naofumi</b></Default>

28
00:01:00,350 --> 00:01:02,830
<Default><b>it won't be long
before the Phoenix revives.</b></Default>

29
00:01:03,189 --> 00:01:05,126
<Default><b>I know that
you're often at odds</b></Default>

30
00:01:05,150 --> 00:01:07,045
<Default><b>but please persuade
the Spear Hero</b></Default>

31
00:01:07,069 --> 00:01:08,126
<Default><b>while there's time.</b></Default>

32
00:01:08,150 --> 00:01:11,359
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

33
00:01:11,489 --> 00:01:13,329
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Persuade him, huh?</b></Default>

34
00:01:14,450 --> 00:01:16,385
<Default><b>No matter
how many times you ask</b></Default>

35
00:01:16,409 --> 00:01:18,809
<Default><b>I'm not gonna make nice
with those idiots.</b></Default>

36
00:01:19,579 --> 00:01:22,419
<Default><b>[FITORIA ] If the heroes
are busy fighting each other</b></Default>

37
00:01:22,629 --> 00:01:24,469
<Default><b>then you leave
me no choice</b></Default>

38
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:26,800
<Default><b>I must kill all
four of you.</b></Default>

39
00:01:28,260 --> 00:01:29,300
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

40
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:31,040
<Default><b>[inhales]</b></Default>

41
00:01:33,010 --> 00:01:34,775
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] I suppose
I could leave Eclair</b></Default>

42
00:01:34,799 --> 00:01:36,439
<Default><b>in charge of my lands.</b></Default>

43
00:01:37,219 --> 00:01:38,979
<Default><b>Then start
with Motoyasu.</b></Default>

44
00:01:45,980 --> 00:01:48,220
<Default><b>- [wind whooshing]
- [leaves rustling]</b></Default>

45
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:51,069
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

46
00:01:51,319 --> 00:01:53,609
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

47
00:01:53,739 --> 00:01:55,659
<Default><b>[MOTOYASU]
Where'd you all go?</b></Default>

48
00:01:56,989 --> 00:01:58,149
<Default><b>Come back.</b></Default>

49
00:01:58,790 --> 00:01:59,830
<Default><b>Please.</b></Default>

50
00:02:00,659 --> 00:02:01,859
<Default><b>I need you.</b></Default>

51
00:02:03,500 --> 00:02:05,579
<Default><b>Elena. Myne.</b></Default>

52
00:03:38,469 --> 00:03:40,509
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

53
00:03:49,860 --> 00:03:51,650
<Default><b>[OLD LADY]
Hai! Hai!</b></Default>

54
00:03:52,189 --> 00:03:53,319
<Default><b>Haaah!</b></Default>

55
00:03:54,110 --> 00:03:56,110
<Default><b>Keep your
breathing steady now!</b></Default>

56
00:03:56,569 --> 00:03:59,409
<Default><b>Hone your focus</b></Default>

57
00:03:59,490 --> 00:04:01,030
<Default><b>[screams]</b></Default>

58
00:04:01,449 --> 00:04:03,580
<Default><b>[ALL] Hai! Hai!</b></Default>

59
00:04:04,539 --> 00:04:05,539
<Default><b>Haa!</b></Default>

60
00:04:07,539 --> 00:04:09,919
<Default><b>[children giggling]</b></Default>

61
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:13,226
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Hm.</b></Default>

62
00:04:13,250 --> 00:04:15,235
<Default><b>- Thank you!
- How's over there?</b></Default>

63
00:04:15,259 --> 00:04:17,446
<Default><b>- Looking good!
- Let's pick some from there.</b></Default>

64
00:04:17,470 --> 00:04:18,750
<Default><b>- Okay!
- Huh.</b></Default>

65
00:04:18,839 --> 00:04:20,889
<Default><b>Oh, Mr. Naofumi!</b></Default>

66
00:04:21,759 --> 00:04:24,430
<Default><b>Hey, You're to call him
"His Lordship!"</b></Default>

67
00:04:24,509 --> 00:04:26,909
<Default><b>Hey, when's breakfast?
I'm getting hungry!</b></Default>

68
00:04:27,060 --> 00:04:29,060
<Default><b>Yeah, and my
tummy is rumbling!</b></Default>

69
00:04:29,269 --> 00:04:30,576
<Default><b>- [clamoring]
- Fine.</b></Default>

70
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:32,240
<Default><b>I'll get on it, relax.</b></Default>

71
00:04:32,269 --> 00:04:34,610
<Default><b>[cheering]</b></Default>

72
00:04:34,939 --> 00:04:36,045
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA]
It seems like everyone's</b></Default>

73
00:04:36,069 --> 00:04:37,749
<Default><b>settled in nicely here.</b></Default>

74
00:04:37,990 --> 00:04:39,699
<Default><b>Yes. And thanks to that</b></Default>

75
00:04:39,779 --> 00:04:42,175
<Default><b>we should have
the outer walls built soon.</b></Default>

76
00:04:42,199 --> 00:04:44,505
<Default><b>Our problem now
is getting enough money.</b></Default>

77
00:04:44,529 --> 00:04:46,175
<Default><b>There's a lot
here to keep up.</b></Default>

78
00:04:46,199 --> 00:04:47,919
<Default><b>Can't Melromarc help us?</b></Default>

79
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,720
<Default><b>I wouldn't count on it.</b></Default>

80
00:04:49,790 --> 00:04:51,605
<Default><b>Every nation
is still rebuilding</b></Default>

81
00:04:51,629 --> 00:04:53,146
<Default><b>from the
Spirit Tortoise.</b></Default>

82
00:04:53,170 --> 00:04:54,170
<Default><b>I see.</b></Default>

83
00:04:54,459 --> 00:04:56,300
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

84
00:04:57,550 --> 00:04:58,950
<Default><b>Oh, how'd it go?</b></Default>

85
00:04:59,550 --> 00:05:01,710
<Default><b>Resetting Fohl
and Sadeena's levels?</b></Default>

86
00:05:02,089 --> 00:05:03,889
<Default><b>We managed
to get it done.</b></Default>

87
00:05:04,139 --> 00:05:07,060
<Default><b>They need to do some rehab
to make up for lost levels.</b></Default>

88
00:05:07,810 --> 00:05:09,810
<Default><b>But from the look of it</b></Default>

89
00:05:10,810 --> 00:05:12,836
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA]
Both of them have come so far</b></Default>

90
00:05:12,860 --> 00:05:14,980
<Default><b>and in such a short amount
of time.</b></Default>

91
00:05:15,649 --> 00:05:16,915
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Unlike your stats</b></Default>

92
00:05:16,939 --> 00:05:18,586
<Default><b>whatever skills
you obtain from training</b></Default>

93
00:05:18,610 --> 00:05:20,450
<Default><b>aren't lost
during a reset.</b></Default>

94
00:05:21,490 --> 00:05:22,740
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

95
00:05:22,870 --> 00:05:25,675
<Default><b>But we gotta get their stats
back up for the Phoenix.</b></Default>

96
00:05:25,699 --> 00:05:28,136
<Default><b>The real problem comes
once they hit their limits.</b></Default>

97
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:30,250
<Default><b>If they do</b></Default>

98
00:05:30,959 --> 00:05:32,599
<Default><b>[sighs]
Yeah, probably.</b></Default>

99
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:34,920
<Default><b>Hey, is the
food ready yet?</b></Default>

100
00:05:35,170 --> 00:05:37,750
<Default><b>I'm so hungry</b></Default>

101
00:05:38,009 --> 00:05:39,855
<Default><b>Food will be ready
in a few minutes</b></Default>

102
00:05:39,879 --> 00:05:41,196
<Default><b>go work up an appetite.</b></Default>

103
00:05:41,220 --> 00:05:42,509
<Default><b>Fine.</b></Default>

104
00:05:44,139 --> 00:05:46,470
<Default><b>I wish we could
just eat right now.</b></Default>

105
00:05:46,759 --> 00:05:49,680
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

106
00:05:50,269 --> 00:05:51,309
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

107
00:05:51,639 --> 00:05:53,939
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

108
00:05:56,939 --> 00:05:58,110
<Default><b>[drooling]</b></Default>

109
00:05:58,899 --> 00:06:00,360
<Default><b>My goodness!</b></Default>

110
00:06:00,439 --> 00:06:02,719
<Default><b>I could eat all the food
on this table!</b></Default>

111
00:06:02,910 --> 00:06:04,836
<Default><b>It's too early
to start drinking.</b></Default>

112
00:06:04,860 --> 00:06:06,386
<Default><b>You don't think
I know that?</b></Default>

113
00:06:06,410 --> 00:06:08,199
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

114
00:06:12,209 --> 00:06:13,959
<Default><b>- Hm.
- Uh...</b></Default>

115
00:06:14,459 --> 00:06:16,139
<Default><b>Sorry, but who are you?</b></Default>

116
00:06:16,250 --> 00:06:17,690
<Default><b>My name is S'yne.</b></Default>

117
00:06:18,839 --> 00:06:19,839
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

118
00:06:21,459 --> 00:06:23,509
<Default><b>Hey! You're
the clown girl</b></Default>

119
00:06:23,589 --> 00:06:26,139
<Default><b>- Clown girl?
- Filo, you know her?</b></Default>

120
00:06:26,470 --> 00:06:28,790
<Default><b>We both already
know her, right, Master?</b></Default>

121
00:06:29,100 --> 00:06:30,780
<Default><b>This should remind you.</b></Default>

122
00:06:31,930 --> 00:06:33,076
<Default><b>[both gasp]</b></Default>

123
00:06:33,100 --> 00:06:35,310
<Default><b>You're Murder Clown!
Why're you here?</b></Default>

124
00:06:35,899 --> 00:06:38,299
<Default><b>- I walked.
- That's not what I asked you.</b></Default>

125
00:06:38,689 --> 00:06:40,779
<Default><b>- Did you come here to eat?
- Yes.</b></Default>

126
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:43,779
<Default><b>Just so you know</b></Default>

127
00:06:43,990 --> 00:06:45,505
<Default><b>At least for
you it's not.</b></Default>

128
00:06:45,529 --> 00:06:46,886
<Default><b>[S'YNE]
I understand.</b></Default>

129
00:06:46,910 --> 00:06:48,949
<Default><b>Is this enough?
For food?</b></Default>

130
00:06:49,620 --> 00:06:51,160
<Default><b>[Filo gasps]</b></Default>

131
00:06:51,750 --> 00:06:54,230
<Default><b>I'm not interested
in taking all your money.</b></Default>

132
00:06:54,329 --> 00:06:56,055
<Default><b>What I'm
trying to say is...</b></Default>

133
00:06:56,079 --> 00:06:56,959
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

134
00:06:57,040 --> 00:06:59,050
<Default><b>Please, just
leave the village.</b></Default>

135
00:06:59,250 --> 00:07:01,970
<Default><b>But it was me who protected
everyone from slavers?</b></Default>

136
00:07:02,300 --> 00:07:04,300
<Default><b>- So why?
- Master Naofumi?</b></Default>

137
00:07:04,379 --> 00:07:06,339
<Default><b>Don't care. I
can't trust you.</b></Default>

138
00:07:07,930 --> 00:07:08,930
<Default><b>I see.</b></Default>

139
00:07:09,310 --> 00:07:12,019
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

140
00:07:14,850 --> 00:07:15,730
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

141
00:07:15,850 --> 00:07:18,019
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

142
00:07:33,500 --> 00:07:34,500
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

143
00:07:35,329 --> 00:07:38,079
<Default><b>Oh, right, Filo, I have
some good news for you.</b></Default>

144
00:07:38,500 --> 00:07:40,820
<Default><b>I'll tell you
after we finish breakfast.</b></Default>

145
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:41,920
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

146
00:07:42,379 --> 00:07:45,339
<Default><b>Carriage! Carriage!
Carriage! Carriage! Carriage!</b></Default>

147
00:07:46,050 --> 00:07:47,589
<Default><b>It's my carriage!</b></Default>

148
00:07:49,300 --> 00:07:50,660
<Default><b>Hooray! Hooray!</b></Default>

149
00:07:51,470 --> 00:07:52,910
<Default><b>[chuckles] Right.</b></Default>

150
00:07:53,519 --> 00:07:55,326
<Default><b>Remember to
raise your levels.</b></Default>

151
00:07:55,350 --> 00:07:57,230
<Default><b>- I know, I know.
- Yes, sir!</b></Default>

152
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:59,375
<Default><b>We'll train our
very hardest!</b></Default>

153
00:07:59,399 --> 00:08:00,480
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

154
00:08:00,610 --> 00:08:03,505
<Default><b>And in the meantime, you'll be
training with me, Rishia.</b></Default>

155
00:08:03,529 --> 00:08:05,529
<Default><b>- [gasps]
- I'll help out, too.</b></Default>

156
00:08:05,779 --> 00:08:07,199
<Default><b>[crying]</b></Default>

157
00:08:07,649 --> 00:08:09,005
<Default><b>And most importantly</b></Default>

158
00:08:09,029 --> 00:08:11,029
<Default><b>don't let anyone
suspicious in.</b></Default>

159
00:08:11,199 --> 00:08:12,555
<Default><b>Just leave it to us.</b></Default>

160
00:08:12,579 --> 00:08:14,370
<Default><b>- Let's go.
- 'Kay!</b></Default>

161
00:08:14,540 --> 00:08:16,055
<Default><b>- Good luck, you guys!
- Bye now!</b></Default>

162
00:08:16,079 --> 00:08:17,685
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA]
We'll be back soon, everyone!</b></Default>

163
00:08:17,709 --> 00:08:20,709
<Default><b>[humming]</b></Default>

164
00:08:20,790 --> 00:08:23,800
<Default><b>[wheels rattling]</b></Default>

165
00:08:25,209 --> 00:08:26,355
<Default><b>It's been so long</b></Default>

166
00:08:26,379 --> 00:08:28,699
<Default><b>since we've been
on a journey like this.</b></Default>

167
00:08:28,839 --> 00:08:30,615
<Default><b>It reminds me
of when we met.</b></Default>

168
00:08:30,639 --> 00:08:32,239
<Default><b>I know what you mean.</b></Default>

169
00:08:32,389 --> 00:08:34,826
<Default><b>Maybe we can do some trading
on the way back.</b></Default>

170
00:08:34,850 --> 00:08:36,930
<Default><b>- [FILO] Yay!
- [RAPHTALIA] Great!</b></Default>

171
00:08:37,769 --> 00:08:39,049
<Default><b>[door creaks]</b></Default>

172
00:08:41,059 --> 00:08:42,099
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

173
00:08:44,519 --> 00:08:47,110
<Default><b>How on Earth
did I ever end up like this?</b></Default>

174
00:08:48,529 --> 00:08:51,740
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

175
00:08:51,909 --> 00:08:54,870
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

176
00:08:59,169 --> 00:09:00,769
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA]
This is...</b></Default>

177
00:09:01,419 --> 00:09:02,515
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Yeah.</b></Default>

178
00:09:02,539 --> 00:09:05,169
<Default><b>But we need to find
the Cardinal Hero.</b></Default>

179
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:07,186
<Default><b>[SHOPKEEPER 04-A (M)]
Oh, you'll want to go</b></Default>

180
00:09:07,210 --> 00:09:08,855
<Default><b>to the next street over.</b></Default>

181
00:09:08,879 --> 00:09:10,316
<Default><b>Thank you so much.</b></Default>

182
00:09:10,340 --> 00:09:12,179
<Default><b>Yes, I think
I saw a hero</b></Default>

183
00:09:12,259 --> 00:09:14,859
<Default><b>at one of the taverns
on the outskirts of town.</b></Default>

184
00:09:15,220 --> 00:09:16,380
<Default><b>Thank you.</b></Default>

185
00:09:19,100 --> 00:09:21,060
<Default><b>This should be
the one, right?</b></Default>

186
00:09:21,850 --> 00:09:23,810
<Default><b>[MOTOYASU]
Elena, you're alive!</b></Default>

187
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:26,690
<Default><b>Thank goodness.
I thought I lost you!</b></Default>

188
00:09:26,899 --> 00:09:28,940
<Default><b>Oh, well</b></Default>

189
00:09:29,110 --> 00:09:30,820
<Default><b>I-Is something wrong?</b></Default>

190
00:09:31,159 --> 00:09:32,926
<Default><b>I'm not sure
what to tell you.</b></Default>

191
00:09:32,950 --> 00:09:34,135
<Default><b>Listen, Elena.</b></Default>

192
00:09:34,159 --> 00:09:35,926
<Default><b>We've had a lot
of adventures together</b></Default>

193
00:09:35,950 --> 00:09:37,056
<Default><b>haven't we?</b></Default>

194
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:39,370
<Default><b>So come on!
Let's team up again!</b></Default>

195
00:09:39,620 --> 00:09:41,515
<Default><b>I'm sorry, but
I can't do that.</b></Default>

196
00:09:41,539 --> 00:09:43,265
<Default><b>- [gasps]
- I had to take over</b></Default>

197
00:09:43,289 --> 00:09:44,645
<Default><b>the family business.</b></Default>

198
00:09:44,669 --> 00:09:46,015
<Default><b>- Good day.
- [gasps]</b></Default>

199
00:09:46,039 --> 00:09:47,919
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

200
00:09:48,090 --> 00:09:49,855
<Default><b>If it's party members
that you need</b></Default>

201
00:09:49,879 --> 00:09:51,105
<Default><b>then go to a tavern.</b></Default>

202
00:09:51,129 --> 00:09:53,009
<Default><b>No, see, it
has to be you!</b></Default>

203
00:09:53,090 --> 00:09:54,370
<Default><b>Sir Motoyasu.</b></Default>

204
00:09:54,470 --> 00:09:56,389
<Default><b>Sorry, I mean,
Spear Hero.</b></Default>

205
00:09:56,559 --> 00:09:57,905
<Default><b>I can't bear the idea</b></Default>

206
00:09:57,929 --> 00:09:59,655
<Default><b>of traveling with you
another day.</b></Default>

207
00:09:59,679 --> 00:10:00,679
<Default><b>Elena.</b></Default>

208
00:10:00,769 --> 00:10:02,706
<Default><b>The days when you had
fame and riches</b></Default>

209
00:10:02,730 --> 00:10:04,076
<Default><b>to your name are gone.</b></Default>

210
00:10:04,100 --> 00:10:05,860
<Default><b>And without all that</b></Default>

211
00:10:05,980 --> 00:10:07,899
<Default><b>What do you mean?
I'm a hero!</b></Default>

212
00:10:08,019 --> 00:10:10,086
<Default><b>Please, you're nothing
but a vagrant.</b></Default>

213
00:10:10,110 --> 00:10:11,336
<Default><b>If you want me to return</b></Default>

214
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:12,796
<Default><b>then make something
of yourself.</b></Default>

215
00:10:12,820 --> 00:10:14,860
<Default><b>The same way
the Shield Hero did.</b></Default>

216
00:10:14,950 --> 00:10:15,990
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

217
00:10:18,370 --> 00:10:19,990
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

218
00:10:20,289 --> 00:10:22,500
<Default><b>Huh. N-Naofumi!</b></Default>

219
00:10:22,620 --> 00:10:25,140
<Default><b>Looks like we've
finally found you, Motoyasu!</b></Default>

220
00:10:26,789 --> 00:10:28,590
<Default><b>[grunting]</b></Default>

221
00:10:28,919 --> 00:10:30,299
<Default><b>Hey, wait!</b></Default>

222
00:10:30,710 --> 00:10:32,145
<Default><b>Just hear me out!</b></Default>

223
00:10:32,169 --> 00:10:33,235
<Default><b>Motoyasu!</b></Default>

224
00:10:33,259 --> 00:10:35,090
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

225
00:10:35,799 --> 00:10:37,970
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

226
00:10:38,259 --> 00:10:39,579
<Default><b>Argh, damn it.</b></Default>

227
00:10:40,220 --> 00:10:42,206
<Default><b>Where do you think
he ended up going?</b></Default>

228
00:10:42,230 --> 00:10:43,745
<Default><b>I don't really know.</b></Default>

229
00:10:43,769 --> 00:10:46,399
<Default><b>But there's someone else here
we can talk to.</b></Default>

230
00:10:46,559 --> 00:10:48,019
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

231
00:10:50,730 --> 00:10:52,649
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

232
00:10:52,740 --> 00:10:55,125
<Default><b>I take it you're paying
for all of this, right?</b></Default>

233
00:10:55,149 --> 00:10:57,450
<Default><b>If you tell me
what you know</b></Default>

234
00:10:57,580 --> 00:10:59,200
<Default><b>I will, just relax.</b></Default>

235
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:02,840
<Default><b>What Sir Motoyasu wanted</b></Default>

236
00:11:02,909 --> 00:11:05,989
<Default><b>was to find the Spirit Tortoise
and beat it before you did.</b></Default>

237
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:09,460
<Default><b>[rumbling]</b></Default>

238
00:11:12,090 --> 00:11:14,879
<Default><b>[MOTOYASU] [laughs]
No need to run, men!</b></Default>

239
00:11:14,970 --> 00:11:17,840
<Default><b>I, the Spear Hero</b></Default>

240
00:11:18,090 --> 00:11:20,696
<Default><b>See how much stronger I am
than the Shield Hero!</b></Default>

241
00:11:20,720 --> 00:11:22,326
<Default><b>Time to destroy
this beast!</b></Default>

242
00:11:22,350 --> 00:11:24,550
<Default><b>- [ALL] Right!
- [MOTOYASU] Let's go!</b></Default>

243
00:11:25,019 --> 00:11:26,480
<Default><b>Zweit Hellfire!</b></Default>

244
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:28,899
<Default><b>[fire roaring]</b></Default>

245
00:11:29,860 --> 00:11:31,260
<Default><b>[sword clanging]</b></Default>

246
00:11:32,980 --> 00:11:34,899
<Default><b>You're mine
for the taking!</b></Default>

247
00:11:36,700 --> 00:11:38,779
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

248
00:11:43,539 --> 00:11:44,699
<Default><b>Here goes!</b></Default>

249
00:11:44,950 --> 00:11:46,620
<Default><b>Thunder Spear!</b></Default>

250
00:11:46,870 --> 00:11:48,879
<Default><b>[thunder rumbling]</b></Default>

251
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:51,320
<Default><b>- [electricity crackling]
- [chuckles]</b></Default>

252
00:11:52,340 --> 00:11:54,049
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

253
00:11:54,129 --> 00:11:55,970
<Default><b>[gasps] Wait, what?</b></Default>

254
00:11:56,049 --> 00:11:58,220
<Default><b>- Sir Motoyasu!
- Uh, right!</b></Default>

255
00:11:58,590 --> 00:11:59,970
<Default><b>Meteor Thrust!</b></Default>

256
00:12:00,929 --> 00:12:02,759
<Default><b>[MOTOYASU]
Lightning Spear!</b></Default>

257
00:12:03,850 --> 00:12:05,519
<Default><b>[Motoyasu grunts]</b></Default>

258
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:07,360
<Default><b>- [rumbling]
- [MYNE] Hey.</b></Default>

259
00:12:07,940 --> 00:12:09,780
<Default><b>I don't think
it's working.</b></Default>

260
00:12:10,649 --> 00:12:11,809
<Default><b>[all gasp]</b></Default>

261
00:12:12,860 --> 00:12:15,690
<Default><b>[grunts] Take this!</b></Default>

262
00:12:15,779 --> 00:12:16,859
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

263
00:12:17,110 --> 00:12:17,990
<Default><b>There you have it.</b></Default>

264
00:12:18,110 --> 00:12:20,310
<Default><b>I picked the wrong guy
to suck up to.</b></Default>

265
00:12:20,740 --> 00:12:23,620
<Default><b>Oh, and don't even bother
trying to have me arrested.</b></Default>

266
00:12:23,789 --> 00:12:26,429
<Default><b>I already gave all this info
to the authorities.</b></Default>

267
00:12:26,960 --> 00:12:29,120
<Default><b>What? I told you
everything I know.</b></Default>

268
00:12:29,250 --> 00:12:31,210
<Default><b>Yes, and I do
appreciate that.</b></Default>

269
00:12:31,710 --> 00:12:33,990
<Default><b>Now where are the taverns
in this town?</b></Default>

270
00:12:36,210 --> 00:12:39,220
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

271
00:12:39,429 --> 00:12:40,720
<Default><b>[gurgling]</b></Default>

272
00:12:40,929 --> 00:12:43,929
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

273
00:12:46,350 --> 00:12:47,350
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

274
00:12:47,639 --> 00:12:48,639
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

275
00:12:53,190 --> 00:12:54,730
<Default><b>[gasps] Naofumi.</b></Default>

276
00:12:56,690 --> 00:12:58,740
<Default><b>It's been a while</b></Default>

277
00:13:00,700 --> 00:13:02,385
<Default><b>Hey, relax.
I'm here to talk.</b></Default>

278
00:13:02,409 --> 00:13:04,769
<Default><b>I'm not trying
to arrest you or anything.</b></Default>

279
00:13:05,240 --> 00:13:06,280
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

280
00:13:07,330 --> 00:13:08,730
<Default><b>Filo, Raphtalia.</b></Default>

281
00:13:08,909 --> 00:13:11,289
<Default><b>Sorry, but can you two
look for Motoyasu?</b></Default>

282
00:13:11,580 --> 00:13:12,855
<Default><b>Are you sure?</b></Default>

283
00:13:12,879 --> 00:13:14,525
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Leave us alone for a bit.</b></Default>

284
00:13:14,549 --> 00:13:15,726
<Default><b>Very well, then.</b></Default>

285
00:13:15,750 --> 00:13:16,990
<Default><b>[FILO] Okay.</b></Default>

286
00:13:17,299 --> 00:13:20,299
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

287
00:13:20,970 --> 00:13:22,730
<Default><b>Sit with me
for a second.</b></Default>

288
00:13:26,389 --> 00:13:28,269
<Default><b>I just ran into
Motoyasu.</b></Default>

289
00:13:28,889 --> 00:13:31,535
<Default><b>I think he was here meeting
with an old party member.</b></Default>

290
00:13:31,559 --> 00:13:33,919
<Default><b>But he ran off
before we could even talk.</b></Default>

291
00:13:34,019 --> 00:13:35,019
<Default><b>I see.</b></Default>

292
00:13:35,149 --> 00:13:36,949
<Default><b>So his comrades
are alive.</b></Default>

293
00:13:37,190 --> 00:13:39,150
<Default><b>I heard that
all of yours are.</b></Default>

294
00:13:39,610 --> 00:13:41,810
<Default><b>They're dead.
Every last one of them.</b></Default>

295
00:13:41,899 --> 00:13:43,529
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

296
00:13:47,450 --> 00:13:48,806
<Default><b>It's not my fault.</b></Default>

297
00:13:48,830 --> 00:13:50,385
<Default><b>I lost because
they were weak.</b></Default>

298
00:13:50,409 --> 00:13:51,929
<Default><b>It can't be helped.</b></Default>

299
00:13:52,120 --> 00:13:53,160
<Default><b>[gulps]</b></Default>

300
00:13:53,460 --> 00:13:56,590
<Default><b>[thuds]
It's not, it's not my fault.</b></Default>

301
00:13:58,090 --> 00:14:00,919
<Default><b>Ren, I'm sorry you had
to go through that</b></Default>

302
00:14:01,299 --> 00:14:03,619
<Default><b>but it doesn't mean
you have to give up.</b></Default>

303
00:14:03,720 --> 00:14:06,600
<Default><b>It's only a matter of time
before the Phoenix revives.</b></Default>

304
00:14:07,009 --> 00:14:08,076
<Default><b>When it does</b></Default>

305
00:14:08,100 --> 00:14:10,495
<Default><b>we heroes need to fight
against it together.</b></Default>

306
00:14:10,519 --> 00:14:12,159
<Default><b>Please, fight with me.</b></Default>

307
00:14:13,100 --> 00:14:14,500
<Default><b>[REN] All right.</b></Default>

308
00:14:15,190 --> 00:14:16,230
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

309
00:14:17,149 --> 00:14:19,399
<Default><b>Now then</b></Default>

310
00:14:19,649 --> 00:14:20,649
<Default><b>It...</b></Default>

311
00:14:20,820 --> 00:14:23,460
<Default><b>How dare you put your trust
in the Shield Demon!</b></Default>

312
00:14:23,820 --> 00:14:25,820
<Default><b>[gasps]
Bitch is here?</b></Default>

313
00:14:25,950 --> 00:14:28,110
<Default><b>You told me
that you would trust me!</b></Default>

314
00:14:28,330 --> 00:14:30,676
<Default><b>And that you would believe
what I said, right?</b></Default>

315
00:14:30,700 --> 00:14:32,900
<Default><b>[gasps] I never said
I'd believe you.</b></Default>

316
00:14:33,330 --> 00:14:36,080
<Default><b>And Motoyasu is still looking
for his comrades.</b></Default>

317
00:14:36,169 --> 00:14:38,379
<Default><b>The Spear Hero
is a scumbag</b></Default>

318
00:14:38,750 --> 00:14:40,510
<Default><b>Forget about
him already.</b></Default>

319
00:14:40,549 --> 00:14:42,235
<Default><b>The moment I
laid eyes on you</b></Default>

320
00:14:42,259 --> 00:14:44,775
<Default><b>I knew you were the hero
destined to save the world</b></Default>

321
00:14:44,799 --> 00:14:46,066
<Default><b>unlike the others.</b></Default>

322
00:14:46,090 --> 00:14:48,639
<Default><b>The Spear</b></Default>

323
00:14:49,009 --> 00:14:50,609
<Default><b>just like the Shield.</b></Default>

324
00:14:50,970 --> 00:14:52,730
<Default><b>Motoyasu. That bastard!</b></Default>

325
00:14:53,059 --> 00:14:54,299
<Default><b>Ren, come on</b></Default>

326
00:14:54,480 --> 00:14:56,800
<Default><b>don't tell me
you believe this nonsense.</b></Default>

327
00:14:56,899 --> 00:14:58,625
<Default><b>Remember the trial
at the castle?</b></Default>

328
00:14:58,649 --> 00:15:00,980
<Default><b>Enough with your lies</b></Default>

329
00:15:01,070 --> 00:15:03,005
<Default><b>- Huh?
- That trial was nothing</b></Default>

330
00:15:03,029 --> 00:15:04,755
<Default><b>but a farce
that had been conjured up</b></Default>

331
00:15:04,779 --> 00:15:06,659
<Default><b>to steal the
throne from me!</b></Default>

332
00:15:06,820 --> 00:15:09,450
<Default><b>My mother joined forces
with the Shield Demon</b></Default>

333
00:15:09,539 --> 00:15:12,789
<Default><b>just to humiliate me</b></Default>

334
00:15:12,870 --> 00:15:14,910
<Default><b>in a position
to take the throne!</b></Default>

335
00:15:16,289 --> 00:15:17,976
<Default><b>And the Shield
Demon here</b></Default>

336
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:20,355
<Default><b>was secretly controlling
the Spirit Tortoise</b></Default>

337
00:15:20,379 --> 00:15:22,566
<Default><b>all so he could gain
the people's trust!</b></Default>

338
00:15:22,590 --> 00:15:24,919
<Default><b>Meaning!
He killed your comrades!</b></Default>

339
00:15:25,009 --> 00:15:26,970
<Default><b>[grunts]
Take that back.</b></Default>

340
00:15:27,470 --> 00:15:28,905
<Default><b>[REN]
Is that true Naofumi?</b></Default>

341
00:15:28,929 --> 00:15:29,809
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Seriously?</b></Default>

342
00:15:29,889 --> 00:15:31,929
<Default><b>I can prove to you
I'm not lying.</b></Default>

343
00:15:31,970 --> 00:15:33,655
<Default><b>If I were, my
slave crest</b></Default>

344
00:15:33,679 --> 00:15:35,309
<Default><b>would be activating</b></Default>

345
00:15:35,809 --> 00:15:37,940
<Default><b>[gasps]
How is that possible?</b></Default>

346
00:15:38,519 --> 00:15:40,666
<Default><b>Please, you have
to believe me, Ren.</b></Default>

347
00:15:40,690 --> 00:15:41,930
<Default><b>I do, but...</b></Default>

348
00:15:44,740 --> 00:15:45,755
<Default><b>I care about you</b></Default>

349
00:15:45,779 --> 00:15:47,846
<Default><b>more than anyone
in this world, Ren.</b></Default>

350
00:15:47,870 --> 00:15:49,885
<Default><b>Everyone else may think you
to be a criminal</b></Default>

351
00:15:49,909 --> 00:15:52,349
<Default><b>but I know with all my heart
you're a hero.</b></Default>

352
00:15:52,409 --> 00:15:53,635
<Default><b>- [grunts]
- I believe you fought</b></Default>

353
00:15:53,659 --> 00:15:55,979
<Default><b>for the sake of the world
that day, Ren.</b></Default>

354
00:15:56,120 --> 00:15:57,160
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

355
00:15:58,000 --> 00:15:59,186
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
You wretched.</b></Default>

356
00:15:59,210 --> 00:16:01,840
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

357
00:16:04,379 --> 00:16:07,196
<Default><b>Even if the whole world
were to turn against you, Ren</b></Default>

358
00:16:07,220 --> 00:16:08,946
<Default><b>I would stand
by your side.</b></Default>

359
00:16:08,970 --> 00:16:11,025
<Default><b>My allegiance
is only with you, Ren</b></Default>

360
00:16:11,049 --> 00:16:12,649
<Default><b>the great Sword Hero.</b></Default>

361
00:16:12,929 --> 00:16:14,405
<Default><b>- Shut the hell up!
- [MOTOYASU] Wait!</b></Default>

362
00:16:14,429 --> 00:16:16,230
<Default><b>- [panting]
- Motoyasu?</b></Default>

363
00:16:16,309 --> 00:16:17,365
<Default><b>[both grunt]</b></Default>

364
00:16:17,389 --> 00:16:18,745
<Default><b>What are you
doing with Ren?</b></Default>

365
00:16:18,769 --> 00:16:20,916
<Default><b>I've been looking for you
this whole time!</b></Default>

366
00:16:20,940 --> 00:16:22,940
<Default><b>Please, Myne</b></Default>

367
00:16:23,190 --> 00:16:24,296
<Default><b>Sword Hero!</b></Default>

368
00:16:24,320 --> 00:16:26,029
<Default><b>You heard him just now</b></Default>

369
00:16:26,110 --> 00:16:27,676
<Default><b>He told me he's
looking for me</b></Default>

370
00:16:27,700 --> 00:16:29,046
<Default><b>but called me a whore!</b></Default>

371
00:16:29,070 --> 00:16:30,296
<Default><b>- [gasps]
- That's proof</b></Default>

372
00:16:30,320 --> 00:16:32,096
<Default><b>that he forced
himself on me!</b></Default>

373
00:16:32,120 --> 00:16:35,080
<Default><b>And he told me he'd kill
my father if I tried resisting!</b></Default>

374
00:16:35,330 --> 00:16:36,909
<Default><b>No, that isn't true!</b></Default>

375
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:38,135
<Default><b>[REN]
You really did that?</b></Default>

376
00:16:38,159 --> 00:16:40,370
<Default><b>Of course not!
She's lying to you!</b></Default>

377
00:16:40,629 --> 00:16:41,686
<Default><b>I swear!</b></Default>

378
00:16:41,710 --> 00:16:43,355
<Default><b>[REN]
Why should I trust you?</b></Default>

379
00:16:43,379 --> 00:16:45,316
<Default><b>[MOTOYASU ] Listen to me, Ren!
I never laid a hand</b></Default>

380
00:16:45,340 --> 00:16:47,066
<Default><b>on her or anything like that!
If she hadn't asked me</b></Default>

381
00:16:47,090 --> 00:16:49,330
<Default><b>to wait till dawn
and call the knights</b></Default>

382
00:16:49,470 --> 00:16:50,379
<Default><b>I would've
gladly cut you</b></Default>

383
00:16:50,470 --> 00:16:51,655
<Default><b>- down myself!
- [REN] So you're gonna run away</b></Default>

384
00:16:51,679 --> 00:16:53,235
<Default><b>as soon as things start
to get tough?</b></Default>

385
00:16:53,259 --> 00:16:54,326
<Default><b>You really are scum!</b></Default>

386
00:16:54,350 --> 00:16:55,430
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

387
00:16:56,470 --> 00:16:57,790
<Default><b>I'm impressed.</b></Default>

388
00:16:57,980 --> 00:17:01,559
<Default><b>Who knew one human being
could lie so much, witch.</b></Default>

389
00:17:01,649 --> 00:17:03,206
<Default><b>Hey, stay away
from Myne!</b></Default>

390
00:17:03,230 --> 00:17:04,335
<Default><b>Ren, please.</b></Default>

391
00:17:04,359 --> 00:17:05,835
<Default><b>Don't tell me
you believe a word</b></Default>

392
00:17:05,859 --> 00:17:08,299
<Default><b>coming out of that
lying bitch's big mouth.</b></Default>

393
00:17:08,440 --> 00:17:09,279
<Default><b>Enough!</b></Default>

394
00:17:09,359 --> 00:17:11,160
<Default><b>Myne's right</b></Default>

395
00:17:11,240 --> 00:17:12,886
<Default><b>from the very beginning!</b></Default>

396
00:17:12,910 --> 00:17:14,216
<Default><b>The reason my party died</b></Default>

397
00:17:14,240 --> 00:17:16,055
<Default><b>and I'm being
blamed for it now</b></Default>

398
00:17:16,079 --> 00:17:17,919
<Default><b>is because of
you, Naofumi!</b></Default>

399
00:17:18,079 --> 00:17:19,079
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

400
00:17:20,500 --> 00:17:22,780
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Oh, so that's how it is, huh?</b></Default>

401
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:24,315
<Default><b>If that's how
you're gonna be</b></Default>

402
00:17:24,339 --> 00:17:26,579
<Default><b>I've got some shit
to say to you, too.</b></Default>

403
00:17:26,670 --> 00:17:28,106
<Default><b>Your friends are dead</b></Default>

404
00:17:28,130 --> 00:17:29,446
<Default><b>because you're
treating this</b></Default>

405
00:17:29,470 --> 00:17:31,310
<Default><b>- like a video game.
- What?</b></Default>

406
00:17:31,549 --> 00:17:33,235
<Default><b>But it's not
your fault, right?</b></Default>

407
00:17:33,259 --> 00:17:36,059
<Default><b>Because it's easier to blame
someone else, isn't it?</b></Default>

408
00:17:36,809 --> 00:17:38,649
<Default><b>This world isn't
some game.</b></Default>

409
00:17:38,680 --> 00:17:41,160
<Default><b>You had loyal followers
who believed in you.</b></Default>

410
00:17:41,349 --> 00:17:42,509
<Default><b>And yet...</b></Default>

411
00:17:43,019 --> 00:17:45,139
<Default><b>You're not just a failure
as a hero</b></Default>

412
00:17:45,359 --> 00:17:46,959
<Default><b>but as a human being!</b></Default>

413
00:17:47,819 --> 00:17:48,690
<Default><b>You're wrong!</b></Default>

414
00:17:48,779 --> 00:17:50,755
<Default><b>It's not my fault
they died, dammit!</b></Default>

415
00:17:50,779 --> 00:17:52,255
<Default><b>Stop, Ren! You can't let</b></Default>

416
00:17:52,279 --> 00:17:54,136
<Default><b>the Shield Hero
get in your head!</b></Default>

417
00:17:54,160 --> 00:17:55,216
<Default><b>Get lost, witch!</b></Default>

418
00:17:55,240 --> 00:17:57,320
<Default><b>Before I kill you
where you stand!</b></Default>

419
00:17:58,119 --> 00:17:59,176
<Default><b>You know exactly</b></Default>

420
00:17:59,200 --> 00:18:00,686
<Default><b>what you should be
doing right now.</b></Default>

421
00:18:00,710 --> 00:18:02,726
<Default><b>But here you are
refusing to do it</b></Default>

422
00:18:02,750 --> 00:18:05,515
<Default><b>because it would require you
to admit that you screwed up.</b></Default>

423
00:18:05,539 --> 00:18:06,606
<Default><b>Am I wrong?</b></Default>

424
00:18:06,630 --> 00:18:08,275
<Default><b>How dare you
say that to me?</b></Default>

425
00:18:08,299 --> 00:18:09,985
<Default><b>Need me to say it again?</b></Default>

426
00:18:10,009 --> 00:18:11,889
<Default><b>You know
exactly what to do.</b></Default>

427
00:18:12,049 --> 00:18:14,209
<Default><b>Your conscience
is screaming at you.</b></Default>

428
00:18:14,470 --> 00:18:15,866
<Default><b>But I guess
you're too damn busy</b></Default>

429
00:18:15,890 --> 00:18:17,656
<Default><b>listening to that
lying whore run her mouth</b></Default>

430
00:18:17,680 --> 00:18:19,640
<Default><b>so you can't
hear it, can you?</b></Default>

431
00:18:19,809 --> 00:18:21,390
<Default><b>Shut the hell up!</b></Default>

432
00:18:23,440 --> 00:18:24,480
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

433
00:18:24,559 --> 00:18:26,059
<Default><b>It's not my fault!</b></Default>

434
00:18:26,609 --> 00:18:28,089
<Default><b>It's not my fault!</b></Default>

435
00:18:28,519 --> 00:18:30,559
<Default><b>You're using a skill
in a tavern?</b></Default>

436
00:18:34,609 --> 00:18:36,216
<Default><b>I'm going to
fight for Myne.</b></Default>

437
00:18:36,240 --> 00:18:38,716
<Default><b>For the one person
who still believes in me!</b></Default>

438
00:18:38,740 --> 00:18:40,700
<Default><b>- Stop!
- Meteor Slash!</b></Default>

439
00:18:41,039 --> 00:18:42,119
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

440
00:18:42,750 --> 00:18:44,000
<Default><b>[clamoring]</b></Default>

441
00:18:45,579 --> 00:18:46,939
<Default><b>Master Naofumi!</b></Default>

442
00:18:47,170 --> 00:18:48,839
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

443
00:18:48,960 --> 00:18:51,970
<Default><b>[clamoring]</b></Default>

444
00:18:54,339 --> 00:18:55,339
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

445
00:18:55,430 --> 00:18:57,220
<Default><b>[gasps] Impossible!</b></Default>

446
00:18:57,299 --> 00:18:59,559
<Default><b>Sir Ren, hurry</b></Default>

447
00:19:02,019 --> 00:19:03,325
<Default><b>[REN]
That's not possible.</b></Default>

448
00:19:03,349 --> 00:19:04,876
<Default><b>You have to be cheating!</b></Default>

449
00:19:04,900 --> 00:19:06,166
<Default><b>Face reality, Ren.</b></Default>

450
00:19:06,190 --> 00:19:07,440
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

451
00:19:08,230 --> 00:19:09,590
<Default><b>Flashing Sword!</b></Default>

452
00:19:10,230 --> 00:19:11,550
<Default><b>Wait, hold on!</b></Default>

453
00:19:14,150 --> 00:19:16,160
<Default><b>- Get off me, coward!
- [grunts]</b></Default>

454
00:19:16,700 --> 00:19:18,700
<Default><b>Yeah, that's for
abandoning me!</b></Default>

455
00:19:18,869 --> 00:19:19,869
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

456
00:19:20,200 --> 00:19:22,080
<Default><b>- Do it, Ren!
- Portal Sword!</b></Default>

457
00:19:22,160 --> 00:19:23,200
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

458
00:19:23,750 --> 00:19:24,990
<Default><b>[snickering]</b></Default>

459
00:19:26,460 --> 00:19:27,500
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

460
00:19:27,789 --> 00:19:29,670
<Default><b>- [grunts]
- [fire roaring]</b></Default>

461
00:19:31,880 --> 00:19:33,920
<Default><b>You're the one
who abandoned him.</b></Default>

462
00:19:34,470 --> 00:19:35,525
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA]
Master Naofumi!</b></Default>

463
00:19:35,549 --> 00:19:37,109
<Default><b>- Hm?
- Are you okay?</b></Default>

464
00:19:37,220 --> 00:19:38,220
<Default><b>I am</b></Default>

465
00:19:38,470 --> 00:19:39,750
<Default><b>but he's not.</b></Default>

466
00:19:40,220 --> 00:19:41,059
<Default><b>What did I do?</b></Default>

467
00:19:41,140 --> 00:19:42,616
<Default><b>- Why are Bitch and Elena both?
- [NAOFUMI] Motoyasu!</b></Default>

468
00:19:42,640 --> 00:19:44,406
<Default><b>- [NAOFUMI] Hey, Motoyasu!
- I trusted them with my life.</b></Default>

469
00:19:44,430 --> 00:19:45,706
<Default><b>Why's this happening?</b></Default>

470
00:19:45,730 --> 00:19:47,980
<Default><b>Why is everyone
so cold to me?</b></Default>

471
00:19:48,519 --> 00:19:49,359
<Default><b>I'll never trust</b></Default>

472
00:19:49,440 --> 00:19:50,916
<Default><b>- another woman again.
- Is he going to be okay?</b></Default>

473
00:19:50,940 --> 00:19:52,416
<Default><b>- I don't care.
- Why?</b></Default>

474
00:19:52,440 --> 00:19:54,005
<Default><b>- Can you guys check...
- Why am I the only one stuff</b></Default>

475
00:19:54,029 --> 00:19:56,085
<Default><b>- like this keeps happening to?
- If anyone here is wounded?</b></Default>

476
00:19:56,109 --> 00:19:57,136
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

477
00:19:57,160 --> 00:19:58,505
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
I'm exhausted.</b></Default>

478
00:19:58,529 --> 00:20:01,079
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

479
00:20:05,500 --> 00:20:07,500
<Default><b>[MOTOYASU]
Why am I the only one</b></Default>

480
00:20:07,789 --> 00:20:09,189
<Default><b>this happens to?</b></Default>

481
00:20:09,880 --> 00:20:11,680
<Default><b>Why did this
happen to me.</b></Default>

482
00:20:12,420 --> 00:20:14,970
<Default><b>I never want to talk
to a woman again.</b></Default>

483
00:20:15,170 --> 00:20:18,180
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

484
00:20:18,339 --> 00:20:21,349
<Default><b>[audience cheering]</b></Default>

485
00:21:18,950 --> 00:21:20,230
<Default><b>Is that Filo?</b></Default>

486
00:21:22,069 --> 00:21:23,989
<Default><b>What is this,
Master Naofumi?</b></Default>

487
00:21:24,450 --> 00:21:25,716
<Default><b>Maybe something
she gained</b></Default>

488
00:21:25,740 --> 00:21:27,265
<Default><b>from her time
as a Humming Fairy.</b></Default>

489
00:21:27,289 --> 00:21:29,500
<Default><b>[chomps and chuckles]</b></Default>

490
00:21:31,710 --> 00:21:33,210
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

491
00:21:34,750 --> 00:21:36,476
<Default><b>Here, take
a bite of this!</b></Default>

492
00:21:36,500 --> 00:21:38,020
<Default><b>It'll cheer you up!</b></Default>

493
00:21:41,089 --> 00:21:42,720
<Default><b>[screaming]</b></Default>

494
00:21:43,009 --> 00:21:44,349
<Default><b>Filo!</b></Default>

495
00:21:44,549 --> 00:21:47,930
<Default><b>Filo!</b></Default>

496
00:21:48,019 --> 00:21:50,809
<Default><b>[screaming]</b></Default>

497
00:21:51,559 --> 00:21:52,995
<Default><b>- [Motoyasu grunts]
- [Filo gasps]</b></Default>

498
00:21:53,019 --> 00:21:53,940
<Default><b>Motoyasu...</b></Default>

499
00:21:54,019 --> 00:21:56,099
<Default><b>Glad to see
you're feeling better.</b></Default>

500
00:21:56,269 --> 00:21:58,909
<Default><b>Believe in the method
I gave you to get stronger</b></Default>

501
00:21:58,940 --> 00:22:00,716
<Default><b>and work to get ready
for the fight.</b></Default>

502
00:22:00,740 --> 00:22:02,005
<Default><b>[MOTOYASU]
Understood!</b></Default>

503
00:22:02,029 --> 00:22:03,869
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

504
00:22:07,829 --> 00:22:09,345
<Default><b>This is
everything, isn't it?</b></Default>

505
00:22:09,369 --> 00:22:11,169
<Default><b>What about
the Spear Hero?</b></Default>

506
00:22:11,329 --> 00:22:12,849
<Default><b>From the look of it</b></Default>

507
00:22:12,920 --> 00:22:14,186
<Default><b>to come back with us.</b></Default>

508
00:22:14,210 --> 00:22:15,646
<Default><b>I'll explain what happened
to the Queen</b></Default>

509
00:22:15,670 --> 00:22:17,590
<Default><b>and head back
to the village.</b></Default>

510
00:22:18,460 --> 00:22:21,220
<Default><b>Hey, I want to head back
to the village.</b></Default>

511
00:22:21,670 --> 00:22:23,235
<Default><b>- [door opens]
- [both gasp]</b></Default>

512
00:22:23,259 --> 00:22:25,390
<Default><b>Good morning, Father!
How are you?</b></Default>

513
00:22:25,470 --> 00:22:27,390
<Default><b>- [screams]
- [door closes]</b></Default>

514
00:22:29,099 --> 00:22:30,139
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

515
00:22:30,890 --> 00:22:32,210
<Default><b>What the hell?</b></Default>

516
00:22:32,309 --> 00:22:33,599
<Default><b>Sir! [Thuds]</b></Default>

517
00:22:35,059 --> 00:22:36,956
<Default><b>Your daughter saved me
at my lowest</b></Default>

518
00:22:36,980 --> 00:22:39,150
<Default><b>and she taught me
about true love!</b></Default>

519
00:22:39,569 --> 00:22:41,216
<Default><b>I will give you my word!</b></Default>

520
00:22:41,240 --> 00:22:43,080
<Default><b>I'll keep her happy
forever.</b></Default>

521
00:22:44,279 --> 00:22:46,039
<Default><b>May I have
your blessing?</b></Default>

522
00:22:46,990 --> 00:22:48,030
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

523
00:22:51,329 --> 00:22:55,039
<Default><b>[laughs]
Let's be happy together, Filo!</b></Default>

524
00:22:55,130 --> 00:22:57,356
<Default><b>- [Motoyasu laughing]
- [Filo shrieking]</b></Default>

525
00:22:57,380 --> 00:22:58,880
<Default><b>- [moaning]
- Hey.</b></Default>

526
00:22:59,339 --> 00:23:01,186
<Default><b>Stop it, you're
scaring her!</b></Default>

527
00:23:01,210 --> 00:23:03,930
<Default><b>Stay out of my way</b></Default>

528
00:23:04,089 --> 00:23:05,089
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

529
00:23:05,549 --> 00:23:08,220
<Default><b>[grunts] Pig?</b></Default>

530
00:23:08,720 --> 00:23:10,116
<Default><b>- Huh?
- [thumps]</b></Default>

531
00:23:10,140 --> 00:23:11,956
<Default><b>- [groans]
- All right, let's get going.</b></Default>

532
00:23:11,980 --> 00:23:14,060
<Default><b>- [Filo] 'Kay!
- [Naofumi] Y-Yeah.</b></Default>

533
00:23:14,190 --> 00:23:15,270
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

534
00:23:20,690 --> 00:23:21,730
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

535
00:23:21,900 --> 00:23:23,400
<Default><b>Filo! Filo!</b></Default>

536
00:23:23,740 --> 00:23:25,529
<Default><b>Don't leave me behind!</b></Default>

537
00:23:25,609 --> 00:23:32,619
<Default><b>[crying] Filo!</b></Default>

